original_title: Put It in the Pocket: DC’s Go-Go Music
overview: About a genre of music unique to D.C. called Go-Go. Go-Go music is more than just music to D.C. natives; it’s part of their culture. Get an inside look at the music that shaped D.C.’s culture.
tagline: The music that made DC's culture
title: Put It in the Pocket: DC’s Go-Go Music
